  <brief_title>Efficacy Study of Risedronate to Prevent Cancer Treatment-Induced Bone Loss in Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multicentre Study to Evaluate the Effect of Risedronate and Placebo on Bone Mineral Density in Men Undergoing Androgen Deprivation Therapy With Leuprolide Acetate</official_title>
